Process for C++ file:
1/Launch roscore : $roscore
2/Start the launch file : $roslaunch robot_joy.launch
3/Launch the joy node: $rosrun joy joy_node
  If you want to see the output of the the topic /joy : rostopic echo joy 
4/Start V-rep : $cd /cs-share/pradalier/V-REP
		$sh vrep.sh 
  Choose the scene
  Start simulation

Process for python file:
1/Launch roscore : $roscore
2/Launch the joy node: $rosrun joy joy_node
  If you want to see the output of the the topic /joy : rostopic echo joy
3/Launch the node: $rosrun homework1 robot_joy.py 
4/Start V-rep : $cd /cs-share/pradalier/V-REP
		$sh vrep.sh 
  Choose the scene
  Start simulation
